Package web.gui.secretary

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddSubject
    Add a new subject by inserting information of a subject such as the title, teachers, students of it.
    extends SubjectGUIAbstract class.
    AddUser
    Add a new user (Teacher or Student) by providing full name, user name , and email.
    extends UserGUIAbstract class.
    EditSubject
    Edit information of a subject such as the title, teachers, students of it.
    extends SubjectGUIAbstract class.
    EditUser
    Edit information of a user (Teacher/Student) such as full name, user name, and email.
    extends UserGUIAbstract class.
    EmptyPage
    Welcome page which only display text.
    LoginPanel
    For user (secretary) log in to system by providing user name and password.
    Check the user has to be a secretary in order to log in successfully.
    MainPanel
    the main framework (a JPanel) for the whole web application.
    SubjectItem
    Extends ItemViewAbstract.
    Used in SubjectTab which contains a list of SubjectItem.
    SubjectTab
    Content of page correspond to SubjectTab on the menu bar: List of SubjectItem.
    UserItem
    Extends ItemViewAbstract.
    Used in UserTab which contains a list of UserItem.
    UserTab
    Content of page correspond to UserTab on the menu bar: List of UserItem.
    ViewSubject
    View detail information of title, list of students and list of teachers of a subject .
    ViewUser
    View detail information of full name, user-name and email of a user .
